    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(ST) In Christi nomine. <persName ref="#people/233" key="#Emperor/king"
                            >Berengarius</persName> et <persName ref="#people/234"
                            key="#Emperor/king">Adelbertus</persName> filius eius gracia Dei <rs
                            key="#Emperor/king">reges</rs>, anno regni eorum nono, mense magius,
                        indicione secunda. Constat me <persName key="#siblingOf"><name
                                ref="Ragibertus">Regimbertus</name></persName> qui et Reginzo
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Ursus">Ursoni</name></persName> de <rs
                            key="#Cities">civitate</rs>
                        <placeName ref="#places/10">Bergamo</placeName> accepisem sicuti et in
                        presenciam testium accepi ad te <persName ref="#people/4670"
                            key="#siblingOf">Adremperga</persName>
                        <rs key="#siblingOf">germana</rs> mea <rs key="#Price">argentum quod in
                            valentem per denarios bonos solidos centum</rs>, finitum precium pro <rs
                            key="#Houses">casis</rs> et omnibus rebus <rs key="#Landed_possessions"
                            >teritoris</rs> iuris mei que abere viso sum infra eadem civitatem
                        Bergamo seu foris adque in <rs key="#Vici">vicis</rs> et <rs key="#Fundi"
                            >fundis</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Vici #Fundi">
                            <geogName
                                key="#Cereals #Forests #Hay/fodder #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Fundi #Petiae"
                                ref="#estates/4192">Presidio</geogName></placeName>, <placeName
                            key="#Vici #Fundi"><geogName
                                key="#Cereals #Forests #Hay/fodder #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Fundi #Petiae"
                                ref="#estates/4193">Anteniano</geogName></placeName>, <placeName
                            key="#Vici #Fundi"><geogName
                                key="#Cereals #Forests #Hay/fodder #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Fundi #Petiae"
                                ref="#estates/4194">Pricorio</geogName></placeName>, <placeName
                            key="#Vici #Fundi"><geogName
                                key="#Cereals #Forests #Hay/fodder #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Fundi #Petiae"
                                ref="#estates/4195">Manica</geogName></placeName>, <placeName
                            key="#Vici #Fundi"><geogName
                                key="#Cereals #Forests #Hay/fodder #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Fundi #Petiae"
                                ref="#estates/4196">Pranzanica</geogName></placeName>, <placeName
                            key="#Vici #Fundi"><geogName
                                key="#Cereals #Forests #Hay/fodder #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Fundi #Petiae"
                                ref="#estates/4197">Sauniano</geogName></placeName>, <placeName
                            key="#Vici #Fundi"><geogName
                                key="#Cereals #Forests #Hay/fodder #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Fundi #Petiae"
                                ref="#estates/4198">Gandino</geogName></placeName>, per aliis
                        singulis locis; ut dictum est, tam casis cum aliis edificiis, cum
                        sediminibus seu terris, curteficiis, <rs key="#Cereals">campis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Hay/fodder">pratis, passcuis</rs>, <rs key="#Wine">vineis</rs>,
                            <rs key="#Forests">silvis</rs> ac stellareis, <rs
                            key="#Fruits/vegetables">arboribus</rs>, ripis, ripinis, cultis et
                        incultis, divisis et indivisis, usibus <rs key="#Rivers">aquarum aquarumque
                            ductibus</rs> seo in concillibas locas, omnia et omnibus sicut mihi qui
                        supra vinditori per qualecumque ingenio legibus pertinet aut pertinuit vel
                        pertinere debentur in integrum. Que autem suprascriptis casis et omnibus
                        rebus, qualiter supe-rius legitur, cum superioribus et inferioribus, cum
                        ingresso et accessione sua presenti die in tua qui supra emtrice mea et cui
                        tu dederis vestrisque eredibus persistat potestatem, iure proprietario
                        nomine abendum et faciendum exinde quitquit volueritis sine omni mea et
                        eredibus meis contradicionem. Quidem et spondeo adque promito me ego qui
                        supra vinditor cum meis eredibus tibi qui supra emtrice mea et cui tu
                        dederis vestrisque eredibus suprascriptam vind(icionem) adinplere et ab omni
                        contradicione hominem defensare. Quod si defendere non potuerimus aut contra
                        ac cartola agere quesierimus, tunc<rs key="#Penalty"> in dublum</rs> vobis
                        predicta vind(ita) restituamus, melioratis quam in tempore fuerint aut
                        valuerint sub estimacione in eodem loco; quia sic inter nobis convenit. Acto
                            <placeName>Trasalcio</placeName>. Signum manus suprascripto Regimberti
                        qui ac cartola fieri rogavi et ei relecta est. Signum manibus <persName
                            key="#Witness #siblingOf"><name ref="Petrus">Petri</name></persName> et
                            <persName key="#Witness #siblingOf"><name ref="Agibrandus"
                                >Ageprandi</name></persName> germanis de vico Trasalcio, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Notkerius">Noteheri</name></persName> qui et
                        Nazo filii quondam Petri de vico Cenate <rs key="#Witness">testibus</rs>.
                        Segnum manibus <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Andreas"
                            >Andrei</name></persName> qui et Azo, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Bruningus">Bruningi</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Gausbertus">Gausperti</name></persName> de
                        Brembate Superiore testibus. <persName key="#Notary"><name ref="Senepertus"
                                >Senepertus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> domnorum regum rogatus subscripsi. <persName
                            key="#Notary"><name ref="Totila">Todilio</name></persName> notarius
                        domnorum regum scripsi, post tradita complevi et dedi.</ab>
                </div>
